Text:
You seem to be doing a lot of underground books.
Any chance of Chuck Austen's Strip # 1-12?

It's very adult and raunchy manga-style.  ;-)

Does this one also has stuffs like - 
Govt. and mind control ... 
or
Secret Alien bases on Earth and moon ...
or 
Ufo cover-ups by the secret Govt.

I really like such stuffs :) and read such articles all the time. It would be great if you can find any comics that has all such stuffs.
